    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the ends from your <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then finely slice</p><p>Peel and slice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong> finely into rings</p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
